<br>
Ran across several camps of Recuso, complete with sumgglers, hunters, etc. One named, Gerak Jelin. Found between some rocks behind the encampment at roughly neg 1000, pos 1050<br>
<br>
****<br>
Gerak Jelin regards you indifferently -- You would probably win this fight..it's not certain though.<br>
You say, 'Hail, Gerak Jelin'<br>
Gerak Jelin gasps for air upon hearing your voice.  'Oh, you scared me!  Try not to sneak up on people anymore ok?'<br>
You say, 'So sorry, Gerak Jelin...'<br>
You say, 'What might you be scared of?'<br>
****<br>
<br>
Wouldn't respond to anything else. A Templar also in zone dropped him, reported no faction hit, and no dropped items. Conned light blue to me at 51. All other Recuso were green.<br>
<br>
Killed one random Recuso that was weilding an interesting looking blade:<br>
<br>
****<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:19:43 2001] A Recuso says 'I have nothing left to lose.  Can you say the same?<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:19:43 2001] You backstab A Recuso for 291 points of damage.<br>
(insert running and screaming here)<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:20:12 2001] You backstab A Recuso for 157 points of damage.<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:20:12 2001] You have slain A Recuso!<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:20:12 2001] Your faction standing with The Recuso got worse.<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:20:12 2001] Your faction standing with Hand of Seru got better.<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:20:12 2001] Your faction standing with Heart of Seru got better.<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:20:12 2001] Your faction standing with Eye of Seru got better.<br>
