[Wed Dec 05 19:20:12 2001] A Recuso's corpse falls, looking relieved.<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:20:23 2001] You receive 7 silver from the corpse.<br>
[Wed Dec 05 19:20:44 2001] --You have looted a Combine Gladius.--<br>
****<br>
<br>
Felt bad afterwards - think I'm going to go anti-Seru now <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
